{"tid":2016004,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港製/支那製]除左日清仲有卡樂B","createTime":"2020-05-14T05:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T07:03:30.000Z","uid":230511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"259ccc1f94d8420fc958688ff178428a55552fee","tid":2016004,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:38:41.000Z","msg":"利申美國撚先<br />\n喺美國既我有時會掛住香港野食要買嚟止下思鄉病<br />\n之前合味道post有講過美國買既合味道係全香港製造<br />\n(有巴打講過可能係關稅/品質唔過關問題)<br />\n<br />\n其實除左日清產品仲有卡樂B<br />\n美國唐人超市都可以買到港版卡樂B薯片(即係香港買開既款)同美版卡樂B薯片<br />\n港版卡樂B係支那製就眾所鳩知啦<br />\n但美版卡樂B(下圖)其實係香港製<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0255/1971/8445/products/200-0073-1_707c9d13-8170-47c7-a927-cae6c3971db5_1024x1024.jpg?v=1579276799\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0255%2F1971%2F8445%2Fproducts%2F200-0073-1_707c9d13-8170-47c7-a927-cae6c3971db5_1024x1024.jpg%3Fv%3D1579276799&h=a92316c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n價錢上都係差唔多，但如果係本地大型超市亞洲產品區就只會有美版賣<br />\n但自從知道卡樂B薯片就粟一燒都係支那製我就只買美版同日版了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要係港版支那製熱浪我食親都即刻生飛滋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國薯片我連食成個月大大包咁食都冇事<br />\n我懷疑會唔會支那廠啲油其實係地溝油<br />\n唔知有冇巴打有料爆下<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提仲有魚仔餅，以前食開港版魚仔餅紫菜味(係呀又係支那製)<br />\n食過韓版(韓國製)之後覺得港版個紫菜味好假好怪<br />\n<br />\n最後希望香港人真係有骨氣啲盡量罷買支那製品，為自己健康同安全著想，支那製會爆炸㗎"},{"pid":"34c823f0d7f5b442ebce99d4d5361e8df48be0c4","tid":2016004,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:40:55.000Z","msg":"幾時轉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142a0201d60233ed54cca7a5b122a89c84c9e51c","tid":2016004,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:41:41.000Z","msg":"魚仔餅 港版同韓版好大分別"},{"pid":"4cad63ee48e811da04cb8d0768af1cd96b081d75","tid":2016004,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"熱浪而家都係香港廠出"},{"pid":"403264d8f813eb1ebdb86f841a30b184ee9f0997","tid":2016004,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cad63ee48e811da04cb8d0768af1cd96b081d75","tid":2016004,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"熱浪而家都係香港廠出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"屌點解我喺美國買會係支那製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfeadec00e1291f042217e5785bd064a6f5135f3","tid":2016004,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"403264d8f813eb1ebdb86f841a30b184ee9f0997","tid":2016004,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cad63ee48e811da04cb8d0768af1cd96b081d75","tid":2016004,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"熱浪而家都係香港廠出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"屌點解我喺美國買會係支那製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:23:10.000Z","msg":"淨係知汕頭有個廠<br />\n不過香港市場既熱浪都一直係西貢廠出品"},{"pid":"5d98c2e91015b181aa717f07ac413f532985220a","tid":2016004,"uid":37957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"去759買日本製好過<br />\n好過俾錢藍店四洲賺"},{"pid":"504e3daae2b4335a11333375c6dd460c7021c4ed","tid":2016004,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d98c2e91015b181aa717f07ac413f532985220a","tid":2016004,"uid":37957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"去759買日本製好過<br />\n好過俾錢藍店四洲賺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:03:30.000Z","msg":"好多日資香港代理都係藍到紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}